# CampusFlow — AI-Enabled Online College Program Management System

**CSC322 Project — Phase 2 Design Report**  
**Team:** Kapil Tamang, Ibsan Hossain, Tausif Hassan, Arif  
**Date:** April 20, 2026  
**Version:** 2.0

## Overview
CampusFlow is an AI-enabled web platform that centralizes 
college program management. It supports four user roles — 
Visitor, Student, Instructor, and Registrar — and includes 
course registration, grading, reviews, complaints, graduation, 
and an AI chatbot assistant.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: Streamlit / HTML prototype
- Backend: Python
- Database: Centralized (Firebase / SQL)
- AI: Local Knowledge Base + External LLM fallback

## Core Services
- AuthService
- ApplicationService
- CourseService
- EnrollmentService
- GradeService
- ReviewService
- ComplaintService
- GraduationService
- ChatService
- SessionService

## Running the Prototype
Open `src/index.html` in any browser to view the GUI prototype.

